Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.10,0:24:51.74,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}予君之意  君不知乎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.47,0:24:57.61,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}察其目光  未縈他意
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.93,0:25:02.90,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}宛如待友  毫無二致
